Maintainer: Catherine M. Crespi <ccrespi at ucla.edu>
Description: This package contains functions for performing power and sample size calculations 
    for a variety of different study designs and outcomes. It is a companion to the 
    book 'Power and Sample Size in R' (2025) by Catherine M. Crespi, CRC Press/Chapman & Hall.
